<h2 style="color: #1A1A1A; margin-top: 0;">ID Verification Update</h2>

<p>Dear Customer,</p>

{{#if isApproved}}
<div class="info-box" style="border-left-color: #28a745;">
  <p style="color: #28a745; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px;">Your ID has been verified successfully!</p>
  <p>You can now proceed with your rental bookings.</p>
</div>

<p>Your National ID verification is complete. You are now eligible to rent items from {{businessName}}.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{storeUrl}}/categories?availability=RENTAL_ONLY" class="btn-primary">Browse Rentals</a>
</p>
{{else}}
<div class="info-box" style="border-left-color: #cc0000;">
  <p style="color: #cc0000; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px;">ID Verification was not approved</p>
  {{#if reason}}
  <p><span class="label">Reason:</span> {{reason}}</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p>Unfortunately, we were unable to verify your ID. Please review the reason above and submit a new verification request with the correct information.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{storeUrl}}/account/verification" class="btn-primary">Submit New Verification</a>
</p>
{{/if}}

<p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong style="color: #D4AF37;">{{businessName}} Team</strong>
</p>
